            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>lamb mince </strong>and <strong>curry powder</strong> in a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Massage the meat with clean hands for 1 min (this helps the patties hold their shape whilst cooking) then shape into 1 patty per person– these are your <strong>curried lamb patty[ies]</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
